A probationary period of approximately one (1) month shall then ensue. The
new Recruit shall then post an introductory message upon the private message
board. The initiate period begins from the date of this posting, and is a
period of trial for the player, a time to be spent getting to know the
members of the guild, understanding the guild's practices and policies, and
deciding if the Comrades of Norrath is something the player wishes to become
a part of. Recruits are free to resign their status at any time. At the
conclusion of the probationary period, a vote shall be taken, guildwide.

From: "mycaell" <mycaell.eq@...>
Subject: Beware!

The message about joining a guild and looking all innocent had a
very, very bad magis.32.exe virus attached takes over your mail box
and sends out bad things, corrupts the boot record of your hard
drive. Don't open those attached files without scanning Norton
saved me again.....
